{"tid":1194994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國傳媒關注遊行，路透社：03年來最大規模","createTime":"2019-06-09T13:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T14:19:43.000Z","uid":134071,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6816703ffc069e15f60a34a0e532ee3b3db60f5a","tid":1194994,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190609/s00001/1560076123488/【逃犯條例-反修例遊行】外國傳媒關注-路透社-03年來最大規模-法新社-修例令港人憤怒\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190609%2Fs00001%2F1560076123488%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%91%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8-%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE-03%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1-%E6%B3%95%E6%96%B0%E7%A4%BE-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E4%BB%A4%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%86%A4%E6%80%92&d=QsQvn9KnS4zrnMXWGBKJePUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=e00e5e4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190609%2Fs00001%2F1560076123488%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%91%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8-%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE-03%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1-%E6%B3%95%E6%96%B0%E7%A4%BE-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E4%BB%A4%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%86%A4%E6%80%92&h=fcd4eb01\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190609/s00001/1560076123488/【逃犯條例-反修例遊行】外國傳媒關注-路透社-03年來最大規模-法新社-修例令港人憤怒</a></span><br />\n<br />\n【逃犯條例．反修例遊行】外國傳媒關注 路透社：03年來最大規模 法新社：修例令港人憤怒 (20:23)<br />\n <br />\n民陣今午（9日）舉行反對《逃犯條例》修訂遊行，遊行到立法會，遊行人數眾多，不少外國傳媒紛紛關注。<br />\n<br />\n路透社稱，商界、法律界、宗教界、政界、學生等各方組織都團結起來反對修例，令這次將會成為自2003年推行《基本法》23條本地立法以來，港府所面對過的最大規模遊行；<br />\n<br />\n法新社說，修例令港人為之憤怒，並形容台灣殺人案為「特洛伊木馬」，指出港人憂慮會被內地不透明和政治化的司法體系所影響；<br />\n<br />\n彭博新聞表示，成千上萬名港人走上街頭抗議修例，反映港人對北京日漸干預的憂慮；<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》報道，遊行反映港人對有機會被引渡回內地的擔憂和憤怒，又引述中大政治與行政學系高級講師蔡子強所言，遊行向世界反映了修例並非符合香港市民所願的信息。<br />\n<br />\n台灣中央社指出，民主派反對修例，原因在於不相信中國司法制度，可以保障被移交者的人權，以及擔心成為遣送政治犯的缺口。"},{"pid":"60ab28d8c14c156edd5f6e0d64a0fc5bba12cf91","tid":1194994,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20976749ba24fc3f2ed9ea42d76301cffa4b4a64","tid":1194994,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:41:17.000Z","msg":"2014年果次唔大過今次??"},{"pid":"82672cfa042254ff94da7185b56bf9526c573858","tid":1194994,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b34082108403279453843e58eed37dd6e49813a","tid":1194994,"uid":29188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:09:50.000Z","msg":"八九年嘅規模"},{"pid":"46f50140865ac278dacf85699ec883d716e3e3e7","tid":1194994,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:18:04.000Z","msg":"特首表示睇唔到"},{"pid":"718f0faee063103655b3f4ffad97cb933525c9b5","tid":1194994,"uid":3704,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"46f50140865ac278dacf85699ec883d716e3e3e7","tid":1194994,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:18:04.000Z","msg":"特首表示睇唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/09/pjsT6t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F09%2FpjsT6t.jpg&h=e4d05121&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}